name: MAGIC ARCADE #1
description:
This is Nyumnya (on the right side) and Muzu (on the left side). 

Nyumnya is a witch who has many abilities, she will helps you with her potion. Muzu, she is Nyumnya's best friend. She always helping Nyumnya, and she was also very patient with her. They both really like to play games, anywhere, anytime. This was one of those moments where they were playing games together at their house. 

But this habit is too much until....
